Subject: [PATCH v3 1/3] ptrace: pass type of a syscall-stop in
 ptrace_message
Message-ID: <20181125020817.7857cc56@akathisia>
In-Reply-To: <20181125020659.785c7b29@akathisia>
References: <20181125020659.785c7b29@akathisia>
